
## 📋 **Barcha API Endpointlar:**

### **1. Students API (v1/)**
- `GET /v1/students` - Barcha talabalar
- `GET /v1/students/{id}` - Bitta talaba
- `GET /v1/students/{id}/attendance` - Talabaning davomati
- `GET /v1/students/{id}/messages` - Talabaga yuborilgan xabarlar
- `POST /v1/students/{id}/attendance` - Davomat qo'yish
- `POST /v1/students/{id}/messages` - Xabar yuborish
- `DELETE /v1/students/{id}/messages/{messageId}` - Xabarni o'chirish

### **2. Organizations API (v1/)**
- `GET /v1/organizations` - Barcha tashkilotlar
- `POST /v1/organizations` - Tashkilot yaratish
- `GET /v1/organizations/{id}` - Bitta tashkilot
- `PUT /v1/organizations/{id}` - Tashkilotni yangilash
- `DELETE /v1/organizations/{id}` - Tashkilotni o'chirish
- `GET /v1/organizations/{id}/students` - Tashkilot talabalari

### **3. Attendance API (v1/)**
- `GET /v1/attendance` - Barcha davomatlar
- `POST /v1/attendance` - Davomat qo'shish
- `GET /v1/attendance/{id}` - Bitta davomat
- `PUT /v1/attendance/{id}` - Davomatni yangilash
- `DELETE /v1/attendance/{id}` - Davomatni o'chirish
- `GET /v1/attendance/statistics` - Davomat statistikasi
- `GET /v1/attendance/group/{groupId}/today` - Guruhning bugungi davomati

### **4. Faculties API (v1/)**
- `GET /v1/faculties` - Barcha fakultetlar
- `POST /v1/faculties` - Fakultet yaratish
- `GET /v1/faculties/{id}` - Bitta fakultet
- `PUT /v1/faculties/{id}` - Fakultetni yangilash
- `DELETE /v1/faculties/{id}` - Fakultetni o'chirish
- `GET /v1/faculties/{id}/students` - Fakultet talabalari
- `GET /v1/faculties/{id}/groups` - Fakultet guruhlari

### **5. Tasks API (v1/)**
- `GET /v1/tasks` - Barcha vazifalar
- `POST /v1/tasks` - Vazifa yaratish
- `GET /v1/tasks/{id}` - Bitta vazifa
- `PUT /v1/tasks/{id}` - Vazifani yangilash
- `DELETE /v1/tasks/{id}` - Vazifani o'chirish
- `POST /v1/tasks/{id}/assign` - Vazifani talabalarga biriktirish
- `GET /v1/tasks/{id}/students` - Vazifa talabalari
- `GET /v1/tasks/supervisor/{supervisorId}` - Rahbar vazifalari

### **6. Notifications API (v1/)**
- `GET /v1/notifications` - Barcha bildirishnomalar
- `POST /v1/notifications` - Bildirishnoma yaratish
- `GET /v1/notifications/{id}` - Bitta bildirishnoma
- `PUT /v1/notifications/{id}` - Bildirishnomani yangilash
- `DELETE /v1/notifications/{id}` - Bildirishnomani o'chirish
- `POST /v1/notifications/{id}/read` - O'qilgan deb belgilash
- `POST /v1/notifications/read-all` - Barchasini o'qilgan deb belgilash
- `GET /v1/notifications/unread-count` - O'qilmaganlar soni
- `GET /v1/notifications/recent` - So'nggi bildirishnomalar
- `GET /v1/notifications/user/{userId}` - Foydalanuvchi bildirishnomalari

### **7. Groups API (v1/)**
- `GET /v1/groups/{groupId}/students` - Guruh talabalari
- `POST /v1/groups/students` - Bir necha guruh talabalari

### **8. Student Authentication API (student/)**
- `POST /student/login` - Talaba logini (token kerak emas)
- `POST /student/logout` - Talaba logouti
- `GET /student/profile` - Talaba profili

### **9. Student Portal API (student/portal/)**
- `GET /student/portal/profile` - Portal profili
- `PUT /student/portal/profile` - Profilni yangilash
- `GET /student/portal/attendance` - Davomat tarixi
- `GET /student/portal/attendance/stats` - Davomat statistikasi
- `GET /student/portal/attendance/today` - Bugungi davomat
- `GET /student/portal/organization` - Tashkilot ma'lumotlari
- `PUT /student/portal/organization` - Tashkilot ma'lumotlarini yangilash
- `GET /student/portal/group` - Guruh ma'lumotlari

## 🔐 **Authentication:**
- **Admin API**: `Authorization: Bearer API_TOKEN`
- **Student API**: `Authorization: Bearer STUDENT_TOKEN`

